<div class='dash-header-wrapper'>
    <h2 class='dashboard-header'>Manage Organizations</h2>
</div>
<div class="side-by-side-container">
    <a href="/organizations/new" class = "section-link">
        <div class="side-by-side-section">
            <h2>Start Your Own Organization</h2>
        </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/organizations/join/select" class = "section-link">
        <div class="side-by-side-section">
            <h2>Join an Existing Organization</h2>
        </div>
    </a>    
</div>
<div id="infoModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close">&times;</span>
        <p class = "info-header">Start Your Own Organization:</p>
        <p> This page allows you to choose how you want to go about adding an organization to your dashboard. Starting
            your own organization gives you the ability to customize its properties.
        </p>
        <p class = "info-header">Join An Existing Organization</p>
        <p> Choosing this route allows you to browse public organizations are open.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<button id="infoButton" class="base-icon info-button"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i></button>
<script src="/js/infoModal.js"></script>
